      "width": 560,
      "height": 380,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Suggested Sequence\n\n## Phase 1\n- define Twilite chat mode\n- lock context and authority rules\n- decide what chat can see and do\n\n## Phase 2\n- build chat surface in the Twilite shell\n- implement streaming API\n- make graph-aware prompt assembly work\n\n## Phase 3\n- bridge chat output into graph actions\n- add confirmation UX for mutations\n- tighten guardrails and failure states\n\n## Phase 4\n- add evals and observability\n- measure chat usefulness on real Twilite tasks\n- expand persistence only after the core loop works",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
