        "taskListText": "1. Define the Twilite chat mode and authority contract\n2. Build the ChatGPT-style Twilite chat surface\n3. Define graph-aware context assembly\n4. Implement the server-side chat API and streaming transport\n5. Bridge chat output into graph actions\n6. Add guardrails, evals, and observability for Twilite chat",
